sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Client as Client SDK
    participant Wallet as Wallet/Signer
    participant Server1 as Server 1
    participant Server2 as Server 2
    participant ServerN as Server N
    participant Blockchain
    
    User->>Client: Initialize session
    Client->>Client: Generate ephemeral keypair
    
    Client->>Wallet: Request signature
    Note over Client,Wallet: Message includes:<br/>- User address<br/>- Ephemeral public key<br/>- Timestamp<br/>- TTL
    
    Wallet->>User: Approve signature?
    User->>Wallet: Approve
    Wallet-->>Client: Signed message
    
    par Server 1
        Client->>Server1: POST /session
        Server1->>Server1: Verify signature
        Server1->>Blockchain: Verify address
        Blockchain-->>Server1: Valid
        Server1->>Server1: Create session
        Server1-->>Client: Session ID
    and Server 2
        Client->>Server2: POST /session
        Server2->>Server2: Verify signature
        Server2->>Blockchain: Verify address
        Blockchain-->>Server2: Valid
        Server2->>Server2: Create session
        Server2-->>Client: Session ID
    and Server N
        Client->>ServerN: POST /session
        ServerN->>ServerN: Verify signature
        ServerN->>Blockchain: Verify address
        Blockchain-->>ServerN: Valid
        ServerN->>ServerN: Create session
        ServerN-->>Client: Session ID
    end
    
    Client->>Client: Verify threshold met
    Client-->>User: Session established
    
    Note over Client,ServerN: Session active for TTL duration